about.summary: Feather Helper is a concise interface to cache numpy arrays and pandas dataframes.

name: featherhelper
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "featherhelper" %}
{% set version = "0.0.5" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: aa6a38812a6ed7c2efec976c8c4788a177f5ac06779731dc458323bc60bb97b8

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - numpy
    - pandas
    - feather-format >=0.4.0
    - pyarrow >=0.11.1

test:
  imports:
    - featherhelper

about:
  home: https://github.com/kiwi0fruit/featherhelper
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Feather Helper is a concise interface to cache numpy arrays and pandas dataframes."
  doc_url: https://github.com/kiwi0fruit/featherhelper
  dev_url: https://github.com/kiwi0fruit/featherhelper

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - kiwi0fruit
